        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
You can fear kite at entrance, or for even better exp you can kill the Shadowknight version of the Centi Dators Deep in like I do... Go in AR... go straight then right... go straight until you get to the big ruin thing with a centi in front of it... go all the way back there, no agro from the centi in front of the ruin. Load:

Vex
ToN
Splurt
Pyro
Root of your choice
HS
AL
FD

Pull the one in front of the ruin, root, dot.. proceed to the one in the middle of the big room, always pull to behind the ruin. There are 2 more to your left, 2 more to your right, static pops, watch for the transient patroller roamers, Keep the whole room clear not counting the 2 lighter skinned centis there are toward the stairs opposite to you.

NOTE: This is very easy for me because I have my epic... so I barely use any mana, I also suggest you get the extended affliction 3 bracer before doing this camp, it is essential.

NOTE: This camp is especially nice because you NEVER get Harmtouched... they will always be OOR or out of line of sight.

NOTE: Repop is I beleive 25 minutes, not sure... 6 centis in 25 minutes... may sound odd but this is actually VERY nice exp because they're considerably higher level than the warriors in the ZI and beyond.


Hope this helps out...

